S.FORM: Hans Adam II ryax sa tay 14 nqu tay 2, Hans Adam II, squliq na sezi'. (minhtuw sa kawas tay 1945) mrhuw Liechtenstein ta' misuw hya' ga Hans Adam II, aring ryax tay 13 squ byacing tay 11 sa kawas 1989 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. qnxan nya Hans Adam II maki tay kawas 1967 msqun ki Marie, Princess of Liechtenstein, tehuk misuw qani.
